	tunneling

	* sysconfig/network-scripts/ifdown, sysconfig/network-scripts/ifup, sysconfig/network-scripts/network-functions:
	always call 'ip link set *dev* ${DEVICE}', to avoid confusion with
	other ip parameters (#104187)

