	* rc.d/rc.sysinit:
	add sleep 1 to avoid race (#17842)

	* sysconfig/network-scripts/ifdown-ppp:
	fix redial loop (#17380)

	* rc.d/init.d/halt: add autofs (#17288)

	* rc.d/rc.local:
	touch /var/lock/subsys/local so we only get run once

